Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Grim news on deficit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w6jp
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Feb 1981
President calls in press to break the news that massive deficit will mean tougher cuts. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less